$ PowerShell: lexical structure

*comments* and *→ Windows/PowerShell/language/lexical-structure/token[tokens]* that are seperated by *line terminators* and *white space*.
-
PowerShell does not consider the *line terminator* to be a *white space* except when it is preceded by the backtick character.

sa:
  The → Windows/PowerShell/language[PowerShell language]
